welcome_message_body: Welcome to Severna Park, a charming city known for its picturesque scenery and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our beautiful city has to offer. Welcome to Severna Park!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport serves all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities for passenger convenience.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Lee Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering exclusive services and facilities for private jet travelers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal of Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport is a modern facility with a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is home to several airlines and offers a variety of dining and shopping options for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is the largest concourse at BWI and offers a wide range of services for travelers, including a business center and children's play area.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is the newest concourse at BWI and features modern design and amenities, including a variety of restaurants and retail shops.

wifi.note: Wi-Fi is free for the first 45 minutes, after which a fee may apply.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The oldest and smallest terminal at DCA, serving mainly regional flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: The main terminal at DCA, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal D
terminals.description: The newest and largest terminal at DCA, serving mainly American Airlines flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
